text: A container with #Sinovac #Coronavirus disease (#COVID19) vaccines from #China is being unloaded from a #ThaiAirways aircraft during a #ceremony to mark the arrival of 200,000 doses of #vaccine in #Bangkok, #Thailand on February 24, 2021.
